cu.explanation_en: Setting local_s_portc to 0, which is out of the valid port range (typically 1-65535), causing invalid SCTP port configuration.

du.explanation_en: Setting nr_cellid to -1, which is out of the valid range (typically 0 or positive), causing invalid cell ID configuration.
du.explanation_zh: 将 nr_cellid 设置为 -1，这超出了有效范围（通常为 0 或正数），导致无效的单元 ID 配置。
